Kesalahan Zhao Gan'e

00:21:52.310 --> 00:21:53.710
harus ditanggapi dengan serius.

00:21:53.750 --> 00:21:54.310
Lagu,

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:56.240
Tetapi

